{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B35ThemeDividerComponentTokensProviderC","title":"OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of divider"}]},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"divider"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSHorizontalDivider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"OUDSVerticalDivider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDividerComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"DividerComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"divider"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Divider","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllDividerComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent07DividerB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s9EscapableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for chip component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomDividerComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the chip component tokens you want.","","        override var borderWidth: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthmediumt }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomDividerComponentTokensProvider: ChipComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomDividerComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(divider: CustomDividerComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(divider: CustomDividerComponentTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    let dividerComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own border semantic tokens providers","    let dividerComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider(","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.13.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeDividerComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThe